{
  "texts": [
    "Codebook Variable Category Descriptions Examples Country Country variable to distinguish between states.",
    "\"France\" Region/City Regional or city variable to distinguish specific locations associated with an allegation of GenAI usage.",
    "UC: (Unclear) Variable used to describe an instance of GenAI usage with no clear regional or city affiliation.",
    "VARIOUS: Variable used to describe an instance of GenAI usage that either references various cities, transcends regional borders, or is nationwide.",
    "\"New Delhi\" \"UC\" \"Various\" Type of Usage CC: (Content Creation) Variable used to describe the application of GenAI in creating material or content related to an election."
